title: Google\Cloud\Vision\V1\ProductSearchParams
name: ProductSearchParams
description:
Parameters for a product search request.

Generated from protobuf message google.cloud.vision.v1.ProductSearchParams

Extends \Google\Protobuf\Internal\Message

params.name: data
params.description: Optional. Data for populating the Message object.

params.name: data.bounding_poly
params.description: The bounding polygon around the area of interest in the image. Optional. If it is not specified, system discretion will be applied.

params.name: data.product_set
params.description: The resource name of a [ProductSet][google.cloud.vision.v1.ProductSet] to be searched for similar images. Format is: projects/PROJECT_ID/locations/LOC_ID/productSets/PRODUCT_SET_ID.

params.name: data.product_categories
params.description: The list of product categories to search in. Currently, we only consider the first category, and either "homegoods", "apparel", or "toys" should be specified.

params.name: data.filter
params.description: The filtering expression. This can be used to restrict search results based on Product labels. We currently support an AND of OR of key-value expressions, where each expression within an OR must have the same key. For example, "(color = red OR color = blue) AND brand = Google" is acceptable, but not "(color = red OR brand = Google)" or "color: red".
